OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FITV News' Lauren Ostridge spoke to the
OL,8,Fstaff and volunteers at St Luke's
OL,9,FHospice about the tax rise and what it
OL,10,Fmeans for them.
OL,12,FHospice bosses have warned they'll
OL,13,Fneed to find an additional #130,000 a
OL,14,Fyear to cover the rise in employer's
OL,15,Fnational insurance contributions
OL,16,Fintroduced in the Labour budget.
