OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FSt Luke's Hospice in Winsford provides
OL,8,Fend-of-life care to elderly and
OL,9,Fterminally ill patients, and relies
OL,10,Falmost entirely on public donations to
OL,11,Fstay open.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday 30 October, Rachel Reeves
OL,14,Fannounced an increase to national
OL,15,Finsurance employer contributions by
OL,16,F1.2 percentage points to 15%, which
OL,17,Fwill come into effect from April 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
