OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FWithout further funding, the tax hike
OL,8,Fcould result in St Luke's have to
OL,9,Freduce the number of services they
OL,10,Foffer.
OL,12,FIt means they would no longer be able
OL,13,Fto help people like Vera Rodger's
OL,14,Fhusband Joe.
OL,16,FVera said: "My husband was in for a
OL,17,Fmonth and they were absolutely
OL,18,Ffantastic. They used to have him
OL,19,Fsinging and I just can't put into
OL,20,Fwords how good they were."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
