OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FJoe came into St Luke's with cancer in
OL,8,F2020. Due to the COVID-19 restrictions
OL,9,FVera wasn't able to visit, but thanks
OL,10,Fto the hospice staff he was able to
OL,11,Freturn to his home and spend his last
OL,12,Ffew weeks with his wife before his
OL,13,Fdeath.
OL,15,FVera said: "He had the choice of going
OL,16,Fto the hospital or going to St Luke's,
OL,17,Fand I'm so glad he chose here.
OL,19,F"This is a part of Winsford, people
OL,20,Fwould be lost without it but they
OL,21,Fdon't always get the credit for it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
