OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FSince her husband passed away, Vera
OL,8,Fhas been fundraising for the hospice
OL,9,Fand was shocked to hear how the
OL,10,FGovernment's plans could affect St
OL,11,FLuke's.
OL,13,FShe said: "I'm disgusted with the
OL,14,FLabour Government. (St Luke) needs
OL,15,Fevery penny they can get and the
OL,16,Fcarers deserve medals.
OL,18,F"Anyone I know who has been through St
OL,19,FLuke's has been full of praise for all
OL,20,Fof them."
