OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FDespite providing NHS services, St
OL,8,FLuke's receives just 15% of its
OL,9,Ffunding from the Government and relies
OL,10,Fon public donations to stay open.
OL,12,FNeil said: "We have a duty to balance
OL,13,Fincome and expenditure, and this extra
OL,14,F#130,000 is on top of a minimum wage
OL,15,Fincrease. It puts a lot of strain on
OL,16,Fthe finances.
OL,18,F"There could be a point where we have
OL,19,Fto reduce services."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
