OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,FNeil argues that not only does the
OL,8,FGovernment's tax hike put St Luke's
OL,9,Ffuture in jeopardy, but will also make
OL,10,FLabour's promise to "build an NHS fit
OL,11,Ffor the future."
OL,13,FHe said: "We as a charity see the
OL,14,Fservices that are not being provided,
OL,15,Fand we try to provide those services.
OL,17,F"Our patients come from hospital, or
OL,18,Ffrom home, and we stop them from going
OL,19,Fback into hospital that works
OL,20,Falongside the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
