OL,3,CHospice warns #130,000 national
OL,4,Cinsurance cost will mean 'reduction in
OL,5,Cservices'
OL,7,F"It's end of life care, and everybody
OL,8,Fis going to die. So we need to be
OL,9,Ffunded correctly."
OL,11,FResponding to worries from hospices
OL,12,Fand GPs, the Health Secretary Wes
OL,13,FStreeting said he was looking into
OL,14,Fways to support those affected by the
OL,15,Flatest tax hikes.
